    "content": "Hey! This is my second tab. It's \"Higher\" by Creed and I've been listening to \r\nthese guys since I was little. I found a really good one on the internet but it \r\nonly gave you like 4 or 5 different riffs and just told you the order to play it \r\nin. I can't do that I need the whole song tabbed or I won't even bother, so I \r\ndecided to fix it... Thanks for making the original, Blink182Enema, on tTabs!\r\n\r\n[tab]Intro (no bass at first)\r\nG| -------------------------------------------|\r\nD| -------------------------------------------|\r\nA| --------0~---------------------------------|\r\nD| -00-0~------------5~----5p0-0-0---5p0-0-0--|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Verse x6\r\nG| -------------------------------------------|\r\nD| -------4-5------------------4-5------------|\r\nA| -------------------------------------------|\r\nD| -0~-0~-------5~-5~--7-0~-0~-------5~-5~--7-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Pre-Chorus (So let\u2019s go there...)\r\nG| -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD| -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA| -------------------------------------------------------------5/10-10-10-10-10-10-10------|\r\nD| -4444444444444444-5555555555555555-4444444444444444-55555555------------------------10---|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus 1 (Can you take me higher?)\r\nG| ---------------------------| \r\nD| ---------------------------|\r\nA| ----44-55--------4-5-7-4-5-|\r\nD| -00-------55-00------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus 2 (to a place...)\r\nG| ---------------------------|\r\nD| ---------------------------|\r\nA| ----44-55--------4b--------|\r\nD| -00-------55-00------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus 1 (Can you take me higher?)\r\nG| ---------------------------| \r\nD| ---------------------------|\r\nA| ----44-55--------4-5-7-4-5-|\r\nD| -00-------55-00------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus Ending\r\nG| ---------------------------|\r\nD| ----------